                                        <persName corresp="#p_WCE1">Wilson</persName> dated December
                                    21, 1953. For text, see <ref target="frus1952-54v14p2">
                                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1952–1954, vol.
                                        XIV, Part 2</ref>, p. 1560.</note>
                            </cell>
